text: A person experiencing chest pain should consult a Cardiologist.
A person experiencing skin rash should consult a Dermatologist.
A person experiencing vision problems should consult a Ophthalmologist.
A person experiencing toothache should consult a Dentist.
A person experiencing back pain should consult a Orthopedic.
A person experiencing frequent urination should consult a Urologist.
A person experiencing stomach ache should consult a Gastroenterologist.
A person experiencing fever should consult a General Physician.
A person experiencing anxiety should consult a Psychiatrist.
A person experiencing pregnancy care should consult a Gynecologist.
